</div>

<div class="usefull-tool">
  <p class="title">Rencontrez des journalistes pertinents.</p>
  <p class="subtitle">Trouvez les bonnes personnes à pitcher<br>
  avec une simple recherche par mots clées</p>


  <div class="item_body item_body-right">
    <div class="content">
      <div class="feedback">
        <img alt="Internet" class="feedback_logo" src="https://media.giphy.com/media/WNWWvrj1Byjm/giphy.gif">
        <div class="feedback_blockquote feedback_blockquote-right">
          <p class="feedback_text">I love the philosophy behind<br>
          Jist.press, and it should be the<br>
          mantra for every marketer. Just Do It.<br>
          Don't outsource it.</p>
          <div class="feedback_charlydev">
            <div class="feedback_avatar" style="background-image: url(https://scontent-cdg2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/14203146_10210657910383697_5461220090349365425_n.jpg?oh=83f959dc163661a5120d53a51ec82b4c&oe=588E06DC)">
            </div>
            <p class="feedback_name">Charly Marty, Founder of Internet</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item_img">
      <%= image_tag "screen-product.png" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

